<plot>Antonis' life spins out of control leading to the start of our film where we find him alone in his family's run down beach house, hiding away from the world. He has given up on life and is literally watching the world pass him by. It has been left up to his best friends - two offbeat cupids - to remind him that there are things to live for!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063681</url></doc>
